T16:16:53.000Z","msg":"雜區，傻仔先會走去買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:31:03.000Z","msg":"而家係雜  但係未來會重建"},{"pid":"5c00d2b283a3a559a0ca69f9c9c01dc451740c50","tid":2496224,"uid":239345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6167127daef0d2c78777fe61e1f37b5a952c4047","tid":2496224,"uid":44277,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:16:53.000Z","msg":"雜區，傻仔先會走去買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"Gentrification"},{"pid":"bab0b922397219613186676e4742848320ec76a5","tid":2496224,"uid":362210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c70302ea5d4176e8dfbced75382b43a49ad67490","tid":2496224,"uid":108545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:25:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />英國冇風打"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:31:34.000Z","msg":"會唔會以後有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc159d36711f1333472817b102bd407ff88915c9","tid":2496224,"uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6167127daef0d2c78777fe61e1f37b5a952c4047","tid":2496224,"uid":44277,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:16:53.000Z","msg":"雜區，傻仔先會走去買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:33:21.000Z","msg":"誠哥啲眼光冇死錯人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf905da9543a92fb749f08ea36d214afb3c5f87","tid":2496224,"uid":232795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c70302ea5d4176e8dfbced75382b43a49ad67490","tid":2496224,"uid":108545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:25:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />英國冇風打"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:34:24.000Z","msg":"其實有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冬天周不時有溫帶氣旋<br />\n海邊可以有相當於8號風球既風力<br />\n只係未必持續得耐，大家照返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c40998e1315b22639b9adef7c86b0e38f420c33","tid":2496224,"uid":59298,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZnCEWXouhMypMAhYZkXkHxt8GyC2VuCvZw9cimQ9RRYc?filename=uVsDCzS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuVsDCzS.jpg&h=6cf1b9f8&s={SIZE}\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"e13058372525b9589d818dbf718c6e89bd3cb27b","tid":2496224,"uid":279298,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:22:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ADPuKaB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FADPuKaB.jpg&h=01c851ff&s={SIZE}\" />"}}